data.title: Captain Fizman
data.content:
Because if I can't protect YouTube, you can be damned well sure I'll Avenge it.

This weekend at #vidconau was an awesome time and definitely made me think about a lot of things, honestly there were some ups and downs but overall it was an awesome weekend.

That being said after walking around in my Civil War uniform for the weekend, I am now going to be known as the protector of YouTube, the Captain America of YouTube (hahahaha). Make sure to look out for some content really soon as this journey is going to be such a Marvelous time. 📸@jrod_hd
